title: American horror story coven - Cordelia and queenie save misty
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment:
"when the rest of the world sees a wall, we see a window"
I LOVE THAT LINE
All the seasons were too, but Coven was PARTICULARLY stunning in the camera-work department. Cordelia’s scenes here exemplify that.
Appreciating that even under extreme stress, Cordelia takes this as a teachable moment for Queenie. She looked so proud of herself when Misty revived :).
in the finale of Coven Queenie wasn't able to bring Zoe back to life, I guess in this point Misty was the one who brought herself, again, for the second time.
A witch power will spike under time of crisis queenie most likely only manifested it at that moment but never really gained it .
